<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    {{> head }}
  <head>

  <body>
    <div class="holder">
      {{> notification }}
      {{> header }}
      {{> menu }}
    </div>

    <main>
      <section>
        <div class="wrapper">
          <div class="authorization columns-3">
            <div class="signin-form block">
              <div class="heading-1">
                Anmeldung
              </div>
              <div class="text">
                Melden Sie sich in lhrem Kundenkonto an.
              </div>
              <form action="" method="post">
                <div class="row">
                  <input type="text" name="username" class="input" placeholder="Username oder E-Mail Adresse *" value="" required />
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                  <input type="password" name="password" class="input" placeholder="Ihr Passwort *" value="" required />
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                  <span>*</span> Pflichtfelder
                </div>
                <div class="row remember-me clear">
                  <div class="left">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="remember-me" name="password" />
                    <label for="remember-me">angemeldet bleiben</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="right">
                    <a href="#">Passwort vergessen?</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn-green">anmelden (login)</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>

            <div class="signup-form block">
              <div class="heading-1 text-center">
                Registrierung
              </div>
              <div class="text text-center">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo
                ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis
                dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Donec quam felis, ultricies
                nec, pellentesque eu.
              </div>
              <div class="btn-brown">
                <a href="#">jetzt registrieten!</a>
              </div>
              <div class="picture text-center">
                <img src="img/anmeldung/tea-time.png" alt="It's always tea time" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="signup-form block no-bg">
              <div class="heading-1 text-center">
                Gastbestellung
              </div>
              <div class="text text-center">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo
                ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis
                dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Donec quam felis, ultricies
                nec, pellentesque eu.
              </div>
              <div class="btn-brown">
                <a href="#">n√§chster schritt</a>
              </div>
              <div class="picture text-center">
                <img src="img/anmeldung/sigin-guest.png" class="guest" alt="Guest login" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        {{> advertising-services }}
      </section>
    </main>

    {{> footer }}
    {{> copyright }}
  </body>
</html>
